						<dl>
							<dd><i>For an item that makes shiny Pokémon more common, see <a href="/web/20201001121408/https://essentialsdocs.fandom.com/wiki/Pok%C3%A9_Radar" title="Poké Radar">Poké Radar</a>.</i></dd>
							<dd><i>For changing the properties of an individual Pokémon, see <a href="/web/20201001121408/https://essentialsdocs.fandom.com/wiki/Editing_a_Pok%C3%A9mon" title="Editing a Pokémon">Editing a Pokémon</a>.</i></dd>
